OL,3,CDonaldson to give up Knighthood and
OL,4,Cresigns from privy council
OL,6,FThe paedophile Jeffrey Donaldson has
OL,7,Fasked to forfeit his knighthood
OL,8,Ffollowing his conviction for historic
OL,9,Fchild sex abuse.
OL,11,FThe disgraced former MP and DUP leader
OL,12,Fhas written to the prime minister
OL,13,Fthrough his solicitor offering to
OL,14,Frenounce his knighthood.
OL,16,FAnd a second letter has been sent
OL,17,Findicating his resignation as a privy
OL,18,Fcouncillor.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
