OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1782479950
OL,3,CDonaldson to give up Knighthood and
OL,4,Cresigns from privy council
OL,6,FDonaldson's solicitor John McBurney
OL,7,Fsaid in a statement: "I have this
OL,8,Fafternoon issued a letter signed by
OL,9,FJeffrey Donaldson to the Cabinet
OL,10,FOffice indicating his request to
OL,11,Frenounce and forfeit his knighthood.
OL,13,F"I have also this afternoon issued a
OL,14,Fletter signed by Jeffrey Donaldson to
OL,15,Fthe Privy Council office tending his
OL,16,Fresignation from the Privy Council
OL,17,Fwith immediate effect."
