OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1782479950
OL,3,CDonaldson to give up Knighthood and
OL,4,Cresigns from privy council
OL,6,FThe 63-year-old was jailed on Monday
OL,7,Ffor a string of historic sex offences,
OL,8,Fincluding one of rape, against two
OL,9,Fwomen when they were children.
OL,11,FSpeaking at an event on Wednesday,
OL,12,FNorthern Ireland First Minister
OL,13,FMichelle O'Neill described Donaldson's
OL,14,Fcrimes as "despicable and depraved".
OL,16,F"He stole childhood from two victims,
OL,17,Fand they'll have to deal with the
OL,18,Fconsequences of that all their lives.
OL,20,F"Justice has been done here," she told
OL,21,FUTV.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/5
