OL,3,CDonaldson to give up Knighthood and
OL,4,Cresigns from privy council
OL,6,FThere have been calls for Donaldson to
OL,7,Fbe stripped of the titles after he was
OL,8,Fconvicted on Monday of 18 sex
OL,9,Foffences, including one count of rape,
OL,10,Fagainst two women when they were
OL,11,Fchildren.
OL,13,FThe offences were committed between
OL,14,F1985 and 2008.
OL,16,FThe two victims gave evidence against
OL,17,Fhim during the trial, during which
OL,18,FDonaldson had denied the offences.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/5
